{{ $json.cv_text }}


## AVAILABLE JOB DESCRIPTIONS:
Use the Google Drvie tool to see the list of our current job description files and file IDs. They are each aptly named with a job title in the file name.

Analyze the email context first, and secondly the candidate's CV as a fallback method.
